{"tid":2274452,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(台灣) 呂秀蓮：支持「兩岸統合，一個中華」","createTime":"2020-11-06T12:26:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T15:24:17.000Z","uid":134071,"like":15,"dislike":298,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"b0e6eb4732a5f0b859bb7bab5b98c4a522365b00","tid":2274452,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:26:10.000Z","msg":"美國總統大選目前進入膠著，前副總統呂秀蓮昨（４）日在政論節目《少康戰情室》中，表示台灣常常在美中關係當中選邊站，因此她提出一個概念是「遠親近鄰」的雙兩岸關係，並且把中國稱「兩岸統一，一個中國」的說法，改成「兩岸統合，一個中華」，讓台灣既能親美也能親中。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=843384\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D843384&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9kcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=babea646\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D843384&h=9c7138af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=843384</a>"},{"pid":"85d6e8d44911d8d2390fc9ec0bd1f28d5bf14951","tid":2274452,"uid":134071,"like":52,"dislike":1,"score":51,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:26:32.000Z","msg":"痴撚左線？"},{"pid":"9fe8b3847297a0240167db987739619da36784cc","tid":2274452,"uid":47492,"like":65,"dislike":1,"score":64,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:27:59.000Z","msg":"依條垃圾妒忌小英 妒忌到比人統戰埋"},{"pid":"959e302cf4606ff0376497d530414ff7504ab973","tid":2274452,"uid":134071,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:28:23.000Z","msg":"失去初心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d08d11c064927ee113f59a848a8cfad5f335c37","tid":2274452,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9fe8b3847297a0240167db987739619da36784cc","tid":2274452,"uid":47492,"like":65,"dislike":1,"score":64,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:27:59.000Z","msg":"依條垃圾妒忌小英 妒忌到比人統戰埋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:28:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.